            <div class="tw-flex tw-items-center tw-justify-between tw-mb-3">
                <h2 class="tw-text-sm tw-font-bold tw-text-slate-700 tw-m-0">System Exclusions <span class="tw-text-slate-400 tw-font-normal">(hr_commission_system_exclusions)</span></h2>
